Have you ever thought of controlling any devices by just tweeting .....?
Here is the project by which you can control your home or office appliances by just tweeting.
Just tweet and see the magic.............

I have used an Arduino with ethernet shield to connect the devices with the internet.
Here I am using ThingSpeak(an IOT platform) which has an amazing app called Tweet Control, it provides us the API keys 
which would be placed in the arduino code.
